@NODE MAIN "hotlist.module guide"

@{fg shine}@{b}hotlist.module@{ub} v1.2 (18th October 1996) for @{b}Directory Opus 5.5@{ub}
@{fg fill}Written by @{fg shine}Leo 'Nudel' Davidson@{fg fill} for @{fg shine}Gods'Gift Utilities@{fg text}

A plug-in module for Directory Opus 5.5 to provide user-defined Hotlists
of paths and files in an extremely nice way.

Written entirely in C (many times faster than the older ARexx hotlist).

